### 6. IPC Tail (`kernel/src/ipc/mod.rs`)

**File:** `/Users/kevinbarnard/src/minix-4/kernel/src/ipc/mod.rs` (305+ lines)

**el1_svc_tail** (lines 294-298):
```rust
#[unsafe(no_mangle)]
pub extern "C" fn el1_svc_tail() {
